Class AddressDialog

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.control.Dialog<Address>
mappe.del3.addressregister.ui.AddressDialog
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.event.EventTarget, ConstructAddress
public class AddressDialog
extends javafx.scene.control.Dialog<Address>
implements ConstructAddress
Dialog for both Adding and editing addresses. Implements ConstructAddress for choosing mode (Mode NEW = new address, Mode EDIT = edit address).

      private void constructAddress()
